{"tid":394750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【圓玄學院】抑鬱女子跳「化寶爐」尋死 ","createTime":"2017-09-10T08:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-10T11:29:36.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22caa4164df0ca8fdb452bca2152bde9365c9b00","tid":394750,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"荃灣圓玄學院今早發生的墮化寶爐意外，警方正循自殺方向調查。58歲女事主身體嚴重燒傷，送院搶救後回復清醒。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，女事主單身，與母親居於天水圍嘉湖山莊，有幾兄弟姐妹，經過調查後，發現事發時化寶爐附近只有女事主一人，她只帶備一個購物袋，但並無祭品，加上她的家人表示她最近有抑鬱及不開心情況，所以正循自殺方向調查。"},{"pid":"914baac97dcbe4b942ac00d8e4b31795d22fe315","tid":394750,"uid":130394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"活人獻祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非常有創意"},{"pid":"badb178cb7518babb7d0ece60c46143b3ba52065","tid":394750,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>活人獻祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非常有創意</blockquote><br />\n可能諗住跳落去就直達西方極樂呢"},{"pid":"112c5d413e847ecf777e65bd4790ef28c3ae7944","tid":394750,"uid":10531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"燒到咁比人救返仲慘過死"},{"pid":"8f03e527d4194da48fad2bcc144d327b5e842aad","tid":394750,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:38:47.000Z","msg":"張生出黎未？"},{"pid":"ab10e44ad455dfe3e76ee309ffe1a25ca22e42e2","tid":394750,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"好癲<br />\n諗起都痛"},{"pid":"98260d7fdbcabc824fed8de52f201d41b2e53026","tid":394750,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>活人獻祭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非常有創意</blockquote><br />\n可能諗住跳落去就直達西方極樂呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗住攞宇宙通行證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji